{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-cours-md-js","path":"/2gt/pc/1-Sante/4-Solutions-et-concentration-massique","webpackCompilationHash":"41b6f3e30b482131442a","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"lyceum.fr"}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<!--\n**BO 2011 **:\n\nSavoir qu'une solution contient des molécules ou des ions.\n\nSavoir que la concentration d\\'une solution en espèce dissoute peut\ns\\'exprimer en g.L^-1^ .\n\nConnaître et exploiter l'expression des concentrations massique d'une\nespèce moléculaire ou ionique dissoute.\n\nPratiquer une démarche expérimentale pour déterminer la concentration\nd'une espèce (échelle de teintes, méthode par comparaison). -->\n<h2 id=\"vocabulaire\"><a href=\"#vocabulaire\" aria-label=\"vocabulaire permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Vocabulaire</h2>\n<div class=\"custom-block custom-block-def\"><div class=\"custom-block-heading\">Solution</div><div class=\"custom-block-body\"><p>Une <strong>solution</strong> est un mélange liquide homogène obtenu par dissolution d'un <strong>soluté</strong>(solide, liquide ou gazeux) dans un <strong>solvant</strong>(liquide).</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"custom-block custom-block-def\"><div class=\"custom-block-heading\">Solution aqueuse</div><div class=\"custom-block-body\"><p>Une solution <strong>aqueuse</strong> est une solution dont le solvant est l'<strong>eau</strong>.</p></div></div>\n<h2 id=\"concentration-massique\"><a href=\"#concentration-massique\" aria-label=\"concentration massique permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Concentration massique</h2>\n<div class=\"custom-block custom-block-def\"><div class=\"custom-block-heading\">Concentration massique c<sub>m</sub></div><div class=\"custom-block-body\"><p>La concentration massique est la masse de soluté dissoute rapportée à 1L de solution.</p><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>c</mi><mi>m</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>m</mi><mi>V</mi></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">c_{m} = \\frac{m}{V}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.58056em;vertical-align:-0.15em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">c</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.151392em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault mtight\">m</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.7935600000000003em;vertical-align:-0.686em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.10756em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.22222em;\">V</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.677em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">m</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.686em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div>\n<p><strong>Notations</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>c</mi><mi>m</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">c_{m}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.58056em;vertical-align:-0.15em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">c</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.151392em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault mtight\">m</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>​: Concentration massique en gramme par litre(<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">.</mi><msup><mi>L</mi><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">g.L^{-1}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.008548em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">g</span><span class=\"mord\">.</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">L</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">−</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>)</li>\n<li><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>m</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">m</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.43056em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">m</span></span></span></span>: masse de soluté en gramme(<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>g</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">g</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">g</span></span></span></span>)</li>\n<li><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>V</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">V</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\" style=\"margin-right:0.22222em;\">V</span></span></span></span>: Volume de solution en litre(<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>L</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">L</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathdefault\">L</span></span></span></span>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"préparer-une-solution\"><a href=\"#pr%C3%A9parer-une-solution\" aria-label=\"préparer une solution permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Préparer une solution</h2>\n<p>Il existe deux méthodes de préparation d'une solution :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>la <strong>dissolution</strong> directe du soluté dans le solvant</li>\n<li>la <strong>dilution</strong> d'une solution concentrée par ajout de solvant.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"par-dissolution\"><a href=\"#par-dissolution\" aria-label=\"par dissolution permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Par dissolution</h3>\n<p><strong>Mode opératoire</strong>: <a href=\"http://www.spc.ac-aix-marseille.fr/phy_chi/Menu/Activites_pedagogiques/cap_exp/Pdf/Dissolution.pdf\">http://www.spc.ac-aix-marseille.fr/phy_chi/Menu/Activites_pedagogiques/cap_exp/Pdf/Dissolution.pdf</a></p>\n<div class=\"custom-block custom-block-example\"><div class=\"custom-block-body\"><p>Calculer la masse de glucose nécessaire à la préparation d'une solution de 50 mL ayant une concentration massique de 30 g/L.</p></div></div>\n<h3 id=\"par-dilution\"><a href=\"#par-dilution\" aria-label=\"par dilution permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Par dilution</h3>\n<p><strong>Mode opératoire:</strong>\n<a href=\"http://www.spc.ac-aix-marseille.fr/phy_chi/Menu/Activites_pedagogiques/cap_exp/Pdf/Dilution.pdf\">http://www.spc.ac-aix-marseille.fr/phy_chi/Menu/Activites_pedagogiques/cap_exp/Pdf/Dilution.pdf</a></p>\n<div class=\"custom-block custom-block-example\"><div class=\"custom-block-body\"><p>Quel volume de solution mère prélever pour obtenir 50 mL d'une solution fille à 10 g/L à partir d'une solution à 100 g/L ?</p></div></div>\n<details class=\"custom-block custom-block-plus\"><summary class=\"custom-block-heading\">Vidéos de techniques expérimentales en chimie</summary><div class=\"custom-block-body\"><p>L'académie de Marseille propose des vidéos et des fiches méthodes concernant l'ensemble des techniques expérimentales de chimie au lycée à l'adresse suivante:</p><p><a href=\"http://www.spc.ac-aix-marseille.fr/phy_chi/Menu/Activites_pedagogiques/cap_exp/\">http://www.spc.ac-aix-marseille.fr/phy_chi/Menu/Activites_pedagogiques/cap_exp/</a></p></div></details>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/2018-2019/2gt/pc/1-Sante/4-Solutions-et-concentration-massique/#vocabulaire\">Vocabulaire</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2018-2019/2gt/pc/1-Sante/4-Solutions-et-concentration-massique/#concentration-massique\">Concentration massique</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/2018-2019/2gt/pc/1-Sante/4-Solutions-et-concentration-massique/#pr%C3%A9parer-une-solution\">Préparer une solution</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/2018-2019/2gt/pc/1-Sante/4-Solutions-et-concentration-massique/#par-dissolution\">Par dissolution</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2018-2019/2gt/pc/1-Sante/4-Solutions-et-concentration-massique/#par-dilution\">Par dilution</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"tags":["solution","concentration","solvant","dissolution","soluté","dilution"]},"fields":{"classe":"2gt","chapter":"Solutions et concentration massique","matter":"pc","nChapter":"4","part":"Santé","nPart":"1"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"2gt/pc/1-Sante/4-Solutions-et-concentration-massique","chapter":"Solutions et concentration massique"}}}